 depending on the luminosity and filter used. We also find that a\nshallow imaging survey will require very high angular resolution, whereas a\ndeep imaging survey will be less resolution-dependent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2016 17:12:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 29 Apr 2017 18:52:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-28"}
