ly unstable solutions have been\ndeformed to long-lived pulsating formations whereas stable solutions conserved\ntheir shapes for a long time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2016 17:52:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-31"}
