 methods, and making the cost of computing Brownian\ndisplacements comparable the cost of computing deterministic displacements in\nBD simulations. A high-performance implementation employing non-uniform fast\nFourier transforms implemented on graphics processing units and integrated with\nthe software package HOOMD-blue is used for benchmarking.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2016 20:18:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2017 16:33:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-26"}
